## 0. Purpose

This WBS is the delivery plan and the **task source of truth**. It decomposes every
user-facing flow into function-level work packages so each row is independently
deliverable, testable, and reviewable by an AI agent in a single narrow prompt.

`Layer` column: **BE** (domain/use case/repository/data), **FE** (presentation/UI/state),
**Integration** (spans BE+FE), **Docs**, **Test** (cross-cutting quality gates).

## 1. Status legend

| Status | Meaning |
| --- | --- |
| Specified | Spec exists; implementation needed. |
| Partial | Some pieces exist; incomplete. |
| Implemented | Confirmed by source + tests. |
| Future | Intended later; needs approval. |
| Blocked | Needs a prerequisite decision/schema. |
| Rejected | Out of scope. |
| Ongoing | Continuous gate; never "done". |

